        <tr>
          <td><code className="text-primary bg-secondary px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-mono">watch</code></td>
          <td><code className="text-xs font-mono text-muted-foreground">{{"watch<T>(source, cb: (newVal, oldVal) => void): Effect"}}</code></td>
          <td>Como effect pero solo dispara en cambios, recibe valor anterior y nuevo</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
